Class PortsFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.vmware.nsx_policy.infra.segments.ports.PortsFactory
  • public class PortsFactory
extends java.lang.Object
    PortsFactory is responsible for creating instances of services contained inside the com.vmware.nsx_policy.infra.segments.ports package and also has the subpackages reference to access respective subpackage services.
